field.value:
Recent changes to the dictionaryadapterfactory have led to the:

public <classname>(<wrapped dictionary type> dict)

constructor being generated with the exact type of the supplied dictionary rather than explicitly defining the param as IDictionary or NameValueCollection. Since the Properties dictionary in aspview is a slightly different type to the PropertyBag in Controller, it can't call the ctor correctly. Patch detects if it is an IDictionary or NameValueCollection and creates the constructor parameter with one of those types instead.
